{"tid":799283,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[地產奇案系列] 元朗映御錄二連撻 買家2016入市今放棄交易","createTime":"2018-08-30T03:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T13:46:08.000Z","uid":42921,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"62e947c0762d36524f4bf7c2f546babb377e76bf","tid":799283,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"元朗映御新增撻大訂個案，有2伙2016年成交的單位至本月才終止交易。<br />\n<br />\n成交紀錄冊顯示，映御1座2樓M室，實用面積398平方呎，一名徐氏買家於2016年7月以423.2萬入市，相隔逾兩年，本月13日終止買賣合約，放棄上會，相信已失一成訂金，即約42萬；另1座23樓A室，實用面積306平方呎，同年4月以357.88萬售出，買家同樣於本月13日放棄交易，料損失約35萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2016年買而家起碼賺2成，咁都撻訂咁on9"},{"pid":"eae748c34285233d671a6c086a231fe3ed2bfede","tid":799283,"uid":181905,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"唱淡軍全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa888cbd70c81d8b6c8d3089425c83af596b0e4","tid":799283,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eae748c34285233d671a6c086a231fe3ed2bfede","tid":799283,"uid":181905,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"唱淡軍全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:09:59.000Z","msg":"2016年買，出生都賣得，有乜到時可能平過2016年一成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958a03b5b9dc3e624b0dad597ebf65d91ea4dcb3","tid":799283,"uid":156411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"上會問題多<br />\n做唔到按保 果班人根本唔會有咁多首期"},{"pid":"11df97c9675296cc336f37aea51cfcbd6ae497a3","tid":799283,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b727b977461ab59d10